resources.string: Kana iwe uri kunakidzwa neapp iyi yandakagadzira, ndapota funga nezvekutenga yangu donho app.
App yekupa haina kuita chero chinhu, asi chako mupiro chinondiratidza kuti yangu nguva yakashandiswa kukudziridza emahara, hapana-ads maapps anoongwa.
Kana iwe uri kunakidzwa neapp iyi yandakagadzira, ndapota funga nezvekutenga yangu yekusimudzira app.

Iyo yekuvandudza app inosanganisira kutarisa mabokisi ekumaka kana iwe uchinge wapererwa nemabhiri kana emari, uye kutenga kwako kunondiratidza kuti nguva yangu yakapera kuvandudza emahara, hapana-ads maapps anoongwa.
